Name: Platformer::Execute();
About the game: You are a robot programmer whose objective is to reach the end of each level. Each level will have logic problems for you to solve, and it's up to you to build a path to the end of the level, with as few programming steps as possible. Look for efficiency each level has an optional objective, in which you should take into account the fewest steps your schedule should have.
